Goal: Spawn an entity with a custom tag that drops a certain item on death.

- /itemsummon [coordinates] [entity] [item] [amount]

- Example: /itemsummon ~ ~ ~ minecraft:zombie minecraft:iron_ingot 1

- Make mobs not despawn.
- Add information command about the entities.
- Add server specific data to the entities.



New mod idea:
FTB quest
- Catch specific pokemon
- Kill specific pokemon
- Catch specific pokemon
